channel.title: Help me plzzz =(
channel.description:
I just started this moparscape thing because I had a lvl 80 banned for real world money buying. Im trying to start over in moparscape.. Heres my problem:
I go into the server download thread to download and play with other people in their server. But.. Everytime I log in im the only person there. Ive tried this with many diffrent servers and many of them are on the top 10 so I think its having problems connecting with other people. I also tried the whole" Go to file new IP and NEW PORT" and put in some from a server list but every time I do it says "ERROR CONNECTING TO SERVER- server many be down" Do I have to download something else to play with other people? I already have the JAVA thingy and everything.
